{
 "file": "_STGTR2.bin",
 "source_size": 25340,
 "built_size": 25987,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1152",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就开始吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7fae908e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x115f",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、西玛中佐、这次要我展示些什么好{00}呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7f8e845ef4eefba02e7b9e864ef2aefcce989eab0e8a4e7dde7bde7c700e907050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x119f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才那场虽说是战斗、可终归是一对一的{00}单挑罢了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7b7e876e8b8e7ede7b6ef28e7ff02e7c4e8e2e947e7b6efb6e7beefb6e7b400e918eae7eaefe7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11bd",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真正的实战里、敌人有时也会结成『小{00}队』",
   "zh_hex": "15e820ef3be7b4e87fef28ef3102e7e3efb2e7cbef2de7c0e7e2e868e8370ce83e00e7c90d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11da",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先让我看看、面对这样的对手你打算怎么{00}打",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8be7f9efcce7f6e7f602e862e7bee7b9e7dae7b4e7beef66e7b8e7f5e889e7f2e7bd00e7f50000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1219",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x122c",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛利根！",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e82ee9b806000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x124d",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1278",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若与组成『小队』的敌人正面交战、我方{00}也会蒙受相当的损失",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e832ea0de8370ce83ee7c90de7b4e7e3efb2ef3be862e861ef2802efccefb100e7c0e7e2e942e8c8e8b1ef53e7b4ea28e8a50000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x129d",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么！只要瓦解掉敌方的『小队』就行了{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bdef97ef32ef2ae99fe89de9d3e7e3efb1e7b40ce83ee7c90de7c5efd6e7ba00ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12dc",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瓦解敌方『小队』！玛利根、米加粒子炮{00}、发射！",
   "zh_hex": "15e99fe89de7e3d00ce83ee7c90d06e845e82ee9b802e878e854ec84e886e95a0002e870ac06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x132a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白！米加粒子炮、发射！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e809ef97e878e854ec84e886e95a02e870ef65ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13ac",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战舰等部分单位……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7d4e826ef70efaee918e83409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13bb",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拥有一种名为『间接』的攻击方式、能攻{00}击远处的格子",
   "zh_hex": "15eb35e7cbefb6e7d1e8ace7c10ce8fcefce0de7b4ef67e7ccefb1ea2602e7c6ef6700e7cce94ce903e7b4e824e8860000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13df",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『间接』攻击时、对方无法反击与回避",
   "zh_hex": "150ce8fcefce0def67e7ccef2d02e7beefb1e7dce84ee87ce7cce832ef52efd90000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1402",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可改为执行『散开』指令",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e9f0e7c1e9fcefd60cef68e7fa0de8c0e94e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x141d",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『散开』需周围有空格才可选用",
   "zh_hex": "150cef68e7fa0de92dea5ce9dee7cbe93fe824e836e7c4e966efb30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x143e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "执行后『小队』会就此解散、但作为交换{00}必定回避攻击",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fc9fe7fe0ce83ee7c90de7e2e7c5e7cae89da402e7dbef2fe7c1e861ea7800e860e8678cca9ee7cc00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1483",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方组队时、基本就用『间接』瓦解",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1ea0de7c9ef2d02e829efa6e7c5efb30ce8fcefce0de99fe89d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14cc",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来你挺明白的嘛",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b8eb5cef39e809e7b4e9360000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14da",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、这次就让你实际用一次『间接』来{00}打一仗吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b9e864e7c5e7f9e7b8e87fedc3efb3efb6e8640ce8fcefce0defcf00e7f5efb6ea37e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1515",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我方是组成『小队』的MS、外加一艘能{00}用『间接』的战舰",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb1e7b6ea0de8370ce83ee7c90de7b4efa7ef9e02e8f7e854efb6eb18e7c600efb30ce8fcefce0de7b4ef28e7d40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1534",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "巧妙运用『间接』和『散开』、来打倒我{00}们试试看！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec13ecc7e986efb30ce8fcefce0de7d30cef68e7fa0d02efcfe7f5e848efcc00e7bbe91de91de7f6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1578",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……虽说只是演习、也太不像样了",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e8b8e7edef32e7b6ea2feab602e7c0e86ae7b5e8e9e7dae7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x158b",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "抱歉、西玛中佐、请让我再重来一次",
   "zh_hex": "15e922e92702e7f8e845ef4eefba02e83ae7f9efcce80be8a1efcfefb6e8640000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15bb",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦……有两下子嘛",
   "zh_hex": "15e9190909e7cbe97def4de886e9360000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15e4",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们的本事、能得到您的认可吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4efa6efb802e7c6e80ae7d7e835e7b4e8a0e7c4e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1612",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、是啊、把后背交给你、足够放心了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b6e7c302e81be7fee9e4e861e839e7b802ea1ee920e86ce82de7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x162c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "包括我在内、海兵队全体、就都归你指挥{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15eabbec71efccef29e99a02e91bef93e7c9efb4ef4f02e7c5e840e947e7b8e8c0e94900e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1665",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "彼此彼此、还请多多关照、西玛中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efc9e7caefc9e7ca02e7f7e83ae7e9e7e9e8bbea1a02e7f8e845ef4eefba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1678",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、在那之前……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602ef29e7b7e7cdef5109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x169f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、什么事？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7dde7bdefb8050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16c4",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难得有这机会、我想趁现在把『捕获』也{00}确认一下",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e80ae7cbe7b9e7e4e7e202efcce7e6e9eae82fef29e81b0cefcde9d80de7c000e88ce8a0efb6ef4d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16e6",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能请你讲解一下吗、西玛中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e83ae7b8eba2e89defb6ef4de80202e7f8e845ef4eefba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1714",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e809e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1744",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『捕获』正如其名……",
   "zh_hex": "150cefcde9d80def3be7f0e8cfe8ac09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1758",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是抓住敌方单位、把它据为己有的指令",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e962e859e7e3efb1e918e83402e81be978e8cce7c1e8c9e7cbe7b4e8c0e94e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1771",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先由我们来做个示范、你给我好好看着！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8be8a6efcce7bbefcfe81ce828eab0ec8e02e7b8e839efcce7c7e7c7e7f6e86def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "除战舰等部分单位外、敌方单位都可以{00}『捕获』",
   "zh_hex": "15e974ef28e7d4e826ef70efaee918e834e8f702e7e3efb1e918e834e840e7c4e7f3000cefcde9d80d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17d6",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用三台以上的单位、将受过伤的敌方单位{00}团团围住……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3eaa0ea16e7f3ef4ce7b4e918e83402e84ae8c8ef36e8f9e7b4e7e3efb1e918e83400ea5eea5ee9dee85909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1808",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "菜单上就会显示出『捕获』指令",
   "zh_hex": "15eeade918b2e7c5e7e2ed73eab0af0ccfe9d80de8c0e94e0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x181c",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在此选择并执行『捕获』、就能俘获那台{00}敌方单位",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7cae966eaaae957e9fcefd60cefcde9d80d02e7c5e7c6eadbe9d8e7b7ea1600e7e3efb1e918e8340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1860",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、来捕获！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702efcfefcde9d8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18b7",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是失败时的情形",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6e8a5e88fef2de7b4e88bec670000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c3",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『捕获』失败时、双方都会受损",
   "zh_hex": "150cefcde9d80de8a5e88fef2d02eabcefb1e840e7e2e8c8ea280000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f5",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『捕获』的成功率……",
   "zh_hex": "150cefcde9d80de7b4e837e9b1e9e109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1904",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对方HP越低、包围越多、成功率就越高",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beefb1eed2eed4ea57ec0802eabbe9deea57e7e902e837e9b1e9e1e7c5ea57e8120000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1940",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比如用三台包围时、成功率会是这样……",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e7f0d8eaa0ea16eabbe9deef2d02e837e9b1e9e1e7e2e7b6e7b9e7da0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1974",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要增加包围的单位、成功率就会像这样{00}上升",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2aea3de854eabbe9dee7b4e918e83402e837e9b1e9e1e7c5e7e2e8e9e7b9e7da00ef4ced2b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1990",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就在这个状态下、再『捕获』一次{00}试试看",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5ef29e7b9e828e98be994ef4d02e80b0cefcde9d80defb6e86400e91de91de7f60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19ba",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一次捕获成功了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6e864efcde9d8e837e9b1e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c6",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "俘获的单位会归我军所有、通关之后便可{00}使用",
   "zh_hex": "15eadbe9d8e7b4e918e834e7e2e947efcce7e0e7fbe7cb02ef59e8bbe7cde7fee8fae7c400e83fefb30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a06",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、就是这样",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7c5e7b6e7b9e7da0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a14",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接下来、就让你实际来『捕获』一回吧",
   "zh_hex": "15efceef4defcf02e7c5e7f9e7b8e87fedc3efcf0cefcde9d80defb6ef52e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a47",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这家伙就是练习捕获用的靶子",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dfe7fde7c5e7b6eb13eab6efcde9d8efb3e7b4eec4e8860000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a54",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把它……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81be97809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a81",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用这些去捕获！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3e7b9e8a4e7ebefcde9d8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab8",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不对吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7bee7d0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac5",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再来一次、给我重做！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80befcfefb6e86402e839efcce8a1e81cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1afa",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这次可得给我做好！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e864e7c4e80ae839efcce81ce7c7ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b2f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "干得好",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d3e80ae7c70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b38",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "演习就到此结束、各员、返回母舰！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2feab6e7c5e7d7e7cae868e89502e819e84902eba88ce9d5e7d40600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b70",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……夏亚大佐",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef37e7d6efa5efba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b94",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、怎么了、玛利根？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7f2e7bde7ba02e845e82ee9b8050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bba",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才演习中捕获的那些MS、西玛中佐说{00}就交给我们来用……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836ea2feab6ef4eefcde9d8e7b4e7b7e8a4efa7ef9e02e7f8e845ef4eefbae7ed00e7c5e861e839efcce7bbefcfefb309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bfa",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c02",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "捕获的应该是里克·大魔、和高机动型扎{00}古吧",
   "zh_hex": "15cfe9d8e7b4e873e898e7b6ef31e7d504bee8d802e7d3e812e7e4ef30e977e84b00e84de7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c20",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "直接拿来用也行、不过拿去『改造』、说{00}不定也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e875efcee9a7efcfefb3e7c0efd602e7b5ef36e9a7e7eb0ce9f0e93e0d02e7ed00e7b5e867e7c0e7b5e8850000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c7f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏中登场的大多数单位、都能进行『分{00}解』和『改造』",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eef4ee9a0e876e7b4efa5e7e9e914e918e83402e840e7c6e892efd60cefae00e89d0de7d30ce9f0e93e0d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c9f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『分解』是将单位分解、取出『零件』的{00}指令",
   "zh_hex": "150cefaee89d0de7b6e84ae918e834efaee89d02e987efbe0ceb74e9910de7b400e8c0e94e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cbb",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『改造』则是把机体和『零件』组合、造{00}出新单位的指令",
   "zh_hex": "150ce9f0e93e0dea87e7b6e81be7e4ef4fe7d30ceb74e9910dea0defc002e93e00efbeef8ae918e834e7b4e8c0e94e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cdc",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在后台菜单中选择『MS开发』、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7feea16eeade918c0e966eaaa0c1314e7fae8700d020000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf3",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "选择『机库』、就会……",
   "zh_hex": "15e966eaaa0ce7e4e9b30d02e7c5e7e209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d0a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "进入『机库』画面",
   "zh_hex": "15e892e8910ce7e4e9b30decefe8620000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d1c",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在此选择『分解』、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7cae966eaaa0cefaee89d0d020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d2f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "分解刚捕获的机体、获得『零件』",
   "zh_hex": "15efaee89de8bcefcde9d8e7b4e7e4ef4f02e9d8e80a0ceb74e9910d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d5c",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有一点必须注意……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cbefb6e822e860e9a2eaccef3c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d70",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被『分解』的单位就此消失",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f10cefaee89d0de7b4e918e834e7c5e7cae928e8a50000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d8c",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被『分解』的单位无法复原、请多注意",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f10cefaee89d0de7b4e918e834e7dce84ee9eee8e402e83ae7e9eaccef3c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1daf",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如此获得的『零件』……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0e7cae9d8e80ae7b40ceb74e9910d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dcf",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是『改造』开发新单位的素材",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b60ce9f0e93e0de7fae870ef8ae918e834e7b4ec86ebcf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dec",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用『改造』新造出的单位",
   "zh_hex": "15efb30ce9f0e93e0def8ae93eefbee7b4e918e8340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dfe",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在『MS开发』下的『系统图』中确认",
   "zh_hex": "15ef290cefa7ef9ee7fae8700def4de7b40ce941e929eb2d0def4ee88ce8a00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e21",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、除『改造』之外……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e9740ce9f0e93e0de7cde8f709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e32",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可用『强化』提升单位能力",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efb30ce8ade9a50de821ed2be918e834e7c6efb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e4d",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这种情况会花费补给点、最多可强化到2{00}级",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d1e88be8d0e7e2eb9fe95dea81e839e82202e8c5e7e9e7c4e8ade9a5e7d7ef5f00eaee0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e6e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "活用这些『改造』和『强化』、增强部队{00}、",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d4efb3e7b9e8a40ce9f0e93e0de7d30ce8ade9a50d02ea3de8adef70e7c900020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e8f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能更轻松地推进今后的关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e952e990e9e0bfeaabe892a2e7fee7b4e8bbe80100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec0",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要用分解高机动型扎古所得的『高机动{00}推进器』、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ad8cde89de812e7e4ef30e977e84be84de7fbe80ae7b40ce812e7e4ef3000eaabe892e8c30d0200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ee2",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能通过『改造』入手大魔·拜恩尼希兹",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6ef59ef360ce9f0e93e0de891ef66efa5e8d8ef4be91ae7eee896e87be8560000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f00",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在今后的作战中、它会成为得力的战力",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb9e7fee7b4ef2fef28ef4e02e978e7e2e837e7c1e80aefb0e7b4ef28efb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f33",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8650909e7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f58",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚大佐！雷达上有反应！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6bea306e8afef2bb2e7cbe87ce87306060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6b",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "似乎有一支联邦的巡逻舰队、正朝我们接{00}近过来！",
   "zh_hex": "15e944e933e7cb87e883ef2ed1e7b4ec12ec3fe7d4e7c902ef3beaad8be7bbb70096ef36d906000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fa2",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "巡逻舰队吗……正好是检验演习成果的好{00}对手",
   "zh_hex": "15ec12ec3fe7d4e7c9e8020909ef3be7c7e7b6ee40ea99ea2feab6e837e871e7b4e7c700e7beae000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fc2",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、玛利根！替我联络西玛中佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e845e82ee9b806ea508bef2eeb14e7f8e845c0a30600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd5",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们即刻、以全队迎击联邦的巡逻舰队！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bbe855e91f02e7f3bbe7c9e931e7ccef2ed1e7b4ec12ec3fe7d4e7c906000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x200e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！遵命！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef97ec40e853ef97ef970000"
  }
 ]
}
